{
  "texts": [
    "As a relatively new area of study, there are limited reviews in existing literature on HSI reconstruction from RGB images.",
    "Zhang et al. (2022) explored methods for hyperspectral reconstruction, including prior-based and data-driven approaches.",
    "Chen et al. (2023) offered a comprehensive look at deep learning techniques for hyperspectral super-resolution.",
    "While the reviews provided a broad overview of the reconstruction algorithms, they did not adequately address how these algorithms are being applied to specific domains.",
    "Despite its huge potential in the agri-food sector, there has been no published review specifically dedicated to image reconstruction within this field."
  ]
}